{"lemma":"ضَمَّة","slug":"ضَمَّة","root":"ض.م.م","root_slug":"ض-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-م-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25975","n25985"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"an embracing"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a number of horses assembled from every quarter for a race"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"damma, ḍamma, the diacritic in the Arabic script that represents the vowel /u/, appearing as a small curl placed above a letter: ـُ"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun of the Form I verb ضَمَّ (ḍamma, “to embrace; to gather; to compress the lips”), from the root ض م م (ḍ m m). When used to describe the vowel ـُ (u), ضَمَّة (ḍamma) means “an instance of [lip-]rounding”, since u is the only short vowel in Arabic that is pronounced with lip-rounding."},"ipa":["/dˤam.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25975","headword_ar":"ضَمَّهُ","root":"Dm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~N","text_ar":"ضَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drew it, put it, brought it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gathered it, together; collected it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~a $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"ضَمَّ شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY $aYo'N","text_ar":"اـِلَى شَىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA, K,) [aor. and] inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drew, put,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought, together"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and joined"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjoined"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing to a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Damamotuhu A_ilaY SadoriY","text_ar":"ضَمَمْتُهُ اـِلَى صَدْرِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I drew him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pressed him, to my bosom;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I embraced him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~a Alqawomu","text_ar":"ضَمَّ القَوْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofusahumo","text_ar":"اَنْفُسَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being app. understood, or perhaps it is correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dum~a","text_ar":"ضُمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, collected themselves together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became collected."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aall~ahum~a A@Domumo na$ariY","text_ar":"اَللَّهُمَّ ا@ضْمُمْ نَشَرِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O God, compose what is discomposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disorganized,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bring together what is scattered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of my affairs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K * and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n$r","text_ar":"نشر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dum~a janaAHaka Eani","text_ar":"ضُمَّ جَنَاحَكَ عَنِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Contract thy side from men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be thou gentle, courteous, easy to deal with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compliant, to men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dum~ato Ealayohi","text_ar":"ضُمَّتْ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^anaAmilu","text_ar":"الاَنَامِلُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ends of the fingers were drawn together upon it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 21. [See also a similar phrase in what follows, with the verb in the act. form, virtually meaning the same.]) ―         -b2-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He compacted it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he compressed it."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, comprised it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enclosed it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he grasped it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~a Ealayohi","text_ar":"ضَمَّ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in both of these senses.] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~ato Ealayohi AlA^anaAmilu","text_ar":"ضَمَّتْ عَلَيْهِ الاَنَامِلُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ends of the fingers grasped it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 21. [See a similar phrase above.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~a EalaY AlmaAli","text_ar":"ضَمَّ عَلَى المَالِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grasped"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all the property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~a mino maAlihi","text_ar":"ضَمَّ مِنْ مَالِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took of his property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~a AlHarofa","text_ar":"ضَمَّ الحَرْفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above, a conventional phrase in lexicology and grammar,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pronounced the letter with the vowel-sound termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~","text_ar":"ضَمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he marked the letter with the sign of that vowel-sound."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","MA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n25985","headword_ar":"ضَمَّةٌ","root":"Dm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. un. of 1 (q. v.): and as such signifying]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An embracing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A number of horses assembled from every quarter for a race:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) thus called because so assembled. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [And, as a conventional term in lexicology and grammar, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sign of the vowel-sound termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~","text_ar":"ضَمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]}}